data.description: THIS IS THE ONE! With new paint and captivating curb appeal, this property welcomes you with a striking first impression! Step inside to discover the expansive living area that leads to a gourmet kitchen adorned with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and a double oven. Light flows in from the charming backyard which features real grass, covered patio space, a storage shed and a chicken coop! Retreat to the upstairs level of the home to find a master suite complete with an oversized shower and a generous walk-in closet. Three additional bedrooms, an updated bathroom, and a laundry room complete the upper level. Recently installed Bruno Elite Stairlift ($18,000 value) conveys with the home for ease of access to all levels or can be removed prior to close at buyers' request.
